#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:287
msgid "There is no limit to what we, as Women, can accomplish."
msgstr ""
"Il n'y a pas de limite à ce que nous, en tant que femmes, pouvons accomplir."

#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:294
msgid "Our social networks"
msgstr "Nos réseaux sociaux"

#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:350
#: templates/accounts/login.html:35 templates/accounts/register.html:29
msgid "Return to site"
msgstr "Retour au site"

#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:366
msgid "Welcome back,"
msgstr "Bon retour parmi nous,"

#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:371
msgid ""
"Thank you for being part of the LIONESS Le Magazine des reines community. "
"<br> Together, we amplify Women's voices."
msgstr ""
"Merci de faire partie de la communauté LIONESS Le Magazine des reines. <br> "
"Ensemble, nous amplifions la voix des femmes."

#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:399
msgid "Member since"
msgstr "Membre depuis"

#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:410
msgid "Magazine section"
msgstr "Rubriques du magazine"

#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:417
msgid ""
"Choose a section and click on the section you would like to explore. You "
"will be redirected to a dedicated page containing articles related to that "
"topic."
msgstr ""
"Choisir une rubrique de magazine et cliquez sur la section que vous "
"souhaitez explorer. Vous serez redirigé vers une page dédiée contenant des "
"articles liés à ce sujet."

#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:428
msgid "Choose category"
msgstr "Choisir une catégorie"

#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:514
msgid "Your Activity"
msgstr "Votre activité"

#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:577
msgid "Your writing matters"
msgstr "Votre écriture compte"

#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:579
msgid ""
"Make your voice heard with LIONESS, the magazine for queens. We highlight "
"inspiring stories, authentic journeys, and empowering women from around the "
"world. Submit your article to our editorial team."
msgstr ""
"Faites entendre votre voix avec LIONESS, le magazine des reines. Nous "
"mettons en lumière des histoires inspirantes, des parcours authentiques et "
"des femmes qui s'affirment, partout dans le monde. Soumettez votre article à "
"notre équipe éditoriale."

#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:580
msgid ""
"We Selected content may be published in the magazine and featured to our "
"community."
msgstr ""
"Certains contenus sélectionnés pourront être publiés dans le magazine et mis "
"en avant auprès de notre communauté."

#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:583
msgid "Send your text here"
msgstr "Envoyez votre texte ici"

#: dashboard/templates/dashboard/dashboard.html:596
msgid " 2026 Lioness Magazine. All rights reserved."
msgstr "2026 Lioness Magazine. Tous droits réservés."

#: dashboard/views.py:18
msgid "Articles read"
msgstr "Articles lus"

#: dashboard/views.py:23
msgid "Magazine issues"
msgstr "Numéros du magazine"

