#: templates/home.html:43 templates/home.html:126 templates/home.html:183
#: templates/home.html:403 templates/includes/header.html:59
msgid "Become a member"
msgstr "Devenir membre"

#: templates/home.html:80 templates/home.html:92 templates/home.html:390
#: templates/includes/footer.html:65 templates/includes/header.html:99
#: templates/includes/header.html:144
msgid "About"
msgstr "À propos"

#: templates/home.html:81 templates/home.html:93 templates/home.html:391
#: templates/includes/footer.html:66 templates/includes/header.html:105
#: templates/includes/header.html:150
msgid "Explore"
msgstr "Découvrir"

#: templates/home.html:82 templates/home.html:94 templates/home.html:152
#: templates/includes/header.html:111 templates/includes/header.html:156
msgid "Community"
msgstr "Communauté"

#: templates/home.html:83 templates/home.html:95 templates/home.html:145
#: templates/home.html:392 templates/includes/footer.html:67
#: templates/includes/header.html:117 templates/includes/header.html:162
msgid "Magazine"
msgstr "Magazine"

#: templates/home.html:84 templates/home.html:96
#: templates/includes/footer.html:68 templates/includes/header.html:123
#: templates/includes/header.html:168
msgid "Services"
msgstr "Services"

#: templates/home.html:85 templates/home.html:97
#: templates/includes/footer.html:69 templates/includes/header.html:129
#: templates/includes/header.html:174
msgid "Personalities"
msgstr "Personnalités"

#: templates/home.html:110
msgid ""
"All women are <span class=\"text-gold-custom\">Lionesses</span><br> They are "
"truly queens"
msgstr ""
"Toutes les femmes sont <span class=\"text-gold-custom\">des Lionnes</"
"span><br> Elles sont vraiment des Reines."

#: templates/home.html:117
msgid "is much more than a magazine."
msgstr "n'est pas seulement un magazine."

#: templates/home.html:119
msgid ""
"It is an international community that spotlights influential and high-impact "
"women from every continent."
msgstr ""
"C’est une communauté internationale, qui met en lumière les femmes "
"influentes et exponentielles issues de tous les continents."

#: templates/home.html:121
msgid ""
"We champion women who are resourceful, creative, and committed, sharing "
"inspiring stories, authentic journeys, and meaningful content."
msgstr ""
"Nous valorisons des femmes ingénieuses, créatives et engagées, à travers des "
"récits inspirants, des parcours authentiques et des contenus porteurs de "
"sens."

#: templates/home.html:123
msgid ""
"Joining LIONESS, Le Magazine des Reines, means becoming part of a club that "
"celebrates women, their ambitions, and their impact in a rapidly changing "
"world."
msgstr ""
"Rejoindre LIONESS, Le Magazine des Reines c’est appartenir à un club qui "
"célèbre les femmes, leurs ambitions et leur impact dans un monde en pleine "
"mutation."

#: templates/home.html:125
msgid "See the magazines"
msgstr "Voir les magazines"

#: templates/home.html:139
msgid "A space to inspire, connect, and impact"
msgstr "Un espace pour inspirer, connecter et impacter"

#: templates/home.html:146
msgid ""
"Discover unique content on business, lifestyle, well-being, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Découvrez un contenu unique sur le business, le lifestyle, le bien-être et "
"bien plus encore."

#: templates/home.html:153
msgid ""
"Join a community of ambitious and committed women from around the world."
msgstr ""
"Rejoignez une communauté de femmes ambitieuses et engagées du monde entier."

#: templates/home.html:159
msgid "Business"
msgstr "Business"

#: templates/home.html:160
msgid ""
"Let's celebrate women entrepreneurs and their initiatives that are "
"transforming our societies."
msgstr ""
"Célébrons les femmes entrepreneures et leurs initiatives qui transforment "
"nos sociétés."

#: templates/home.html:166
msgid "Let's talk about it!"
msgstr "Et si on en parlait ?"

#: templates/home.html:167
msgid ""
"A bridge between Africa and its diaspora to share, learn, and collaborate."
msgstr ""
"Un pont entre l'Afrique et sa diaspora pour partager, apprendre et "
"collaborer."

#: templates/home.html:181
msgid "Join a community of women with exponential impact."
msgstr "Rejoignez une communauté de femmes exponentielles."

#: templates/home.html:182
msgid ""
"Networking, experience sharing, influence, and lobbying with influential "
"figures from around the world."
msgstr ""
"Mises en relations, partage d'expériences, influence, lobbying auprès des "
"personnalités influentes du monde entier."

#: templates/home.html:271
msgid "Our services"
msgstr "Nos services"

#: templates/home.html:276
msgid "Featured"
msgstr "Mise en avant"

#: templates/home.html:277
msgid ""
"Influential figures from diverse backgrounds fill the pages of our media "
"outlet."
msgstr ""
"Des personnalités influentes aux profils divers variés inondent les pages de "
"notre média."

#: templates/home.html:283
msgid "Interviews & Profiles"
msgstr "Interviews & portraits"

#: templates/home.html:284
msgid "Authentic stories to inspire and motivate our readers."
msgstr "Des histoires authentiques pour inspirer et motiver nos lecteurs."

#: templates/home.html:290
msgid "Accompaniement"
msgstr "Accompagnement"

#: templates/home.html:291
msgid ""
"If you become a member, you will have access to resources, advice, and tools "
"to boost your business."
msgstr ""
"En devenant membre, vous aurez accès à des ressources, des conseils et des "
"outils pour booster votre activité."

#: templates/home.html:297
msgid "Media and Content"
msgstr "Média & Contenu"

#: templates/home.html:298
msgid ""
"By becoming a member, you will gain access to podcasts, videos, and articles "
"to help you achieve and sustain success."
msgstr ""
"En devenant membre, vous aurez accès à des podcasts, des vidéos et des "
"articles pour entrer et demeurer dans votre succès."

#: templates/home.html:334
msgid "is a publication of Layilab."
msgstr "est une publication de Layilab."

#: templates/home.html:393
msgid "Service"
msgstr "Service"

#: templates/home.html:394
msgid "The Most Impactful Personalities"
msgstr "Les Personnalités les Plus Impactantes"

#: templates/home.html:398
msgid "Stay tuned"
msgstr "Restez à l'écoute"

#: templates/home.html:399
msgid ""
"Become a member of the community that celebrates women worldwide. Together, "
"we are breaking down patriarchal stereotypes."
msgstr ""
"Devenez membre de la communauté qui célèbre les femmes à travers le monde. "
"Ensemble, nous brisons les stéréotypes patriarcaux."

#: templates/home.html:400
msgid "We are moving forward in open collaboration with men."
msgstr "Nous avançons en étroite collaboration avec les hommes."

