#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Access to Calaméo<br>Digital Magazine"
msgid "Access to Calaméo"
msgstr "Accès au Magazine Numérique Calaméo"

#: templates/includes/header.html:25
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Magazine"
msgid "Digital Magazine"
msgstr "Magazine"

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:6
#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:16
msgid "Cookie Policy"
msgstr "Politique relative aux cookies"

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:19
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "This Cookie Policy explains how LIONESS – Le Magazine des Reines\n"
#| "uses cookies and similar technologies when you visit our website."
msgid ""
"This Cookie Policy explains how LIONESS – Le Magazine des Reines\n"
"                    uses cookies and similar technologies when you visit our "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Cette politique relative aux cookies explique comment LIONESS – Le Magazine "
"des Reines\n"
"utilise des cookies et des technologies similaires lorsque vous visitez "
"notre site web."

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:23
msgid "What Are Cookies?"
msgstr "What Are Cookies?"

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:26
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a "
#| "website. They help websites function properly, improve user experience, "
#| "and provide information to website owners."
msgid ""
"Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit\n"
"                    a website. They help websites function properly, improve "
"user\n"
"                    experience, and provide information to website owners."
msgstr ""
"Les cookies sont de petits fichiers texte stockés sur votre appareil lorsque "
"vous visitez un site web. Ils permettent aux sites web de fonctionner "
"correctement, d'améliorer l'expérience utilisateur et de fournir des "
"informations aux propriétaires de sites."

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:31
msgid "Types of Cookies We Use"
msgstr "Types de cookies que nous utilisons"

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:33
msgid "1. Essential Cookies"
msgstr "1. Essential Cookies"

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:36
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly.They "
#| "enable core features such as user authentication, security, and session "
#| "management."
msgid ""
"These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly.\n"
"                    They enable core features such as user authentication, "
"security,\n"
"                    and session management."
msgstr ""
"Ces cookies sont nécessaires au bon fonctionnement du site web. Ils "
"permettent d'assurer des fonctionnalités essentielles telles que "
"l'authentification des utilisateurs, la sécurité et la gestion des sessions."

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:42
msgid "Without these cookies, certain services may not be available."
msgstr ""
"Sans ces cookies, certains services pourraient ne pas être disponibles."

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:48
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "These cookies help us understand how visitors interact with the website "
#| "by collecting anonymous information about page visits, traffic sources, "
#| "and user behavior."
msgid ""
"These cookies help us understand how visitors interact with the\n"
"                    website by collecting anonymous information about page "
"visits,\n"
"                    traffic sources, and user behavior."
msgstr ""
"Ces cookies nous aident à comprendre comment les visiteurs interagissent "
"avec le site web en collectant des informations anonymes sur les visites de "
"pages, les sources de trafic et le comportement des utilisateurs."

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:60
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "These cookies allow the website to remember your preferences, such as "
#| "language settings and display preferences, to provide a more personalized "
#| "experience."
msgid ""
"These cookies allow the website to remember your preferences,\n"
"                    such as language settings and display preferences, to "
"provide\n"
"                    a more personalized experience."
msgstr ""
"These cookies allow the website to remember your preferences, such as "
"language settings and display preferences, to provide a more personalized "
"experience."

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:68
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Some content or services available on our website may be provided by "
#| "third parties. These providers may place cookies on your device to "
#| "support their services."
msgid ""
"Some content or services available on our website may be provided\n"
"                    by third parties. These providers may place cookies on "
"your device\n"
"                    to support their services."
msgstr ""
"Certains contenus ou services disponibles sur notre site web peuvent être "
"fournis par des tiers. Ces prestataires peuvent placer des cookies sur votre "
"appareil pour assurer le fonctionnement de leurs services."

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:91
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings. Most "
#| "browsers allow you to:"
msgid ""
"You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings.\n"
"                    Most browsers allow you to:"
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez gérer ou désactiver les cookies via les paramètres de votre "
"navigateur. La plupart des navigateurs vous permettent de :"

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:104
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Please note that disabling certain cookies may affect the functionality "
#| "of the website."
msgid ""
"Please note that disabling certain cookies may affect the\n"
"                    functionality of the website."
msgstr ""
"Veuillez noter que la désactivation de certains cookies peut affecter le "
"fonctionnement du site web."

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:111
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Cookies may remain on your device for different periods of time. Some "
#| "cookies are deleted when you close your browser, while others remain "
#| "until they expire or are manually deleted."
msgid ""
"Cookies may remain on your device for different periods of time.\n"
"                    Some cookies are deleted when you close your browser, "
"while\n"
"                    others remain until they expire or are manually deleted."
msgstr ""
"Les cookies peuvent rester sur votre appareil pendant des durées variables. "
"Certains cookies sont supprimés lorsque vous fermez votre navigateur, tandis "
"que d'autres subsistent jusqu'à leur expiration ou leur suppression manuelle."

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:119
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "LIONESS reserves the right to update this Cookie Policy at any time. Any "
#| "modifications will be posted on this page.."
msgid ""
"LIONESS reserves the right to update this Cookie Policy at any\n"
"                    time. Any modifications will be posted on this page.."
msgstr ""
"LIONESS se réserve le droit de mettre à jour cette politique relative aux "
"cookies à tout moment. Toute modification sera publiée sur cette page."

#: templates/legals_notices/cookie_policy.html:126
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "If you have any questions regarding this Cookie Policy, please contact us:"
msgid ""
"If you have any questions regarding this Cookie Policy, please\n"
"                    contact us:."
msgstr ""
